This repository contains a sample app that implements MVI architecture using Jetpack Compose, Kotlin, ViewModel, Flow, and etc.

The core stack:

Jetpack Compose
MVI patterns
Navigation Component
Clean Architecture
Repository and UseCase
Hilt
Room


App functionality:

The program shows a list of videos with the following information: - Image, - Title, - Description.
The list is saved locally using Room.

The user can add a new video manually by choosing a photo according to the legend of
the new Photo picker which available on Android 13 and above and by entering a title and description for the video.
The user can delete the video by swiping from right to left.

At the click of a button, the application can dynamically change the theme of the application